        <item>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>No Budget No Recess Act</b></p> <p> This bill amends the Congressional Budget Act of 1974 to prohibit the House of Representatives from considering a resolution to adjourn for more than three days in August until the House has approved all of the annual appropriations bills for the fiscal year that begins on October 1 of the year. (Under current law, this restriction applies only to a recess during July.) </p>]]></text>
